(NULL, '16', '17', 'Improper Use of Lab Equipment', 'Lab equipment is being mishandled, causing some devices to malfunction. It is important that everyone follows the proper usage guidelines to prevent damage and ensure safety.', NULL, 'pending', current_timestamp()),
